flowchart LR
    CPSU[Controller PSU 5V] --> ESP[ESP32-S3 Mini]
    EPSU[LED PSU 5V 10A] --> FMAIN[Main Fuse 10A]
    FMAIN --> TBP[TB1 +5V Feed]
    EPSU --> TBG[TB2 GND Star]

    TBP --> INJ1[Strip Head +5V]

    TBG --> G1[Strip Head GND]

    ESP -->|GPIO33 DATA| RDATA[330R]
    ESP -->|GPIO21 CLK| RCLK[330R]
    RDATA --> LVL[5V Level Shifter]
    RCLK --> LVL
    LVL --> DIN[LED DATA IN]
    LVL --> CIN[LED CLK IN]

    ESP ---|Ground Bridge| TBG
    CAP[1000-2200uF at strip head] --- INJ1
    CAP --- G1
